{"about_the_game":"The vertical scrolling shooter game '.Decluster', originally released for mobile, and its sequel '.Decluster Zero' are now available in one package.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures of '.Decluster'<br />\r\n- Simple 2D shooting game in an arcade style<br />\r\n- &quot;Homing Laser&quot; that combines offense and defense by erasing enemy bullets while attacking<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures of '.Decluster Zero'<br />\r\n- Further evolved homing laser system<br />\r\n- &quot;Capture System&quot; that slows down enemy bullets and turns them into counter lasers<br />\r\n- &quot;Charge System&quot; that quickly recovers the gauge<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdditional Features<br />\r\n- Compatible with controller, mouse + keyboard, and keyboard operation<br />\r\n- Local replay function<br />\r\n- Online rankings<br />\r\n- Support for vertical screen play<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAbout Vertical Screen Play<br />\r\n To play in vertical mode, please rotate the screen in the Windows display settings and set your monitor in a vertical position. Alternatively, you can set the screen mode to windowed in the game's video settings and resize the window like any other application.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: Some displays may be hidden or simplified in vertical screen mode.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Stage 1: Cleared","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3088370/a7fdea9e1c7edf008ac0afa5389ca27cd054e143.jpg"},{"name":"Stage 2: Cleared","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3088370/a7fdea9e1c7edf008ac0afa5389ca27cd054e143.jpg"},{"name":"Stage 3: Cleared","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3088370/a7fdea9e1c7edf008ac0afa5389ca27cd054e143.jpg"},{"name":"Stage 4: Cleared","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3088370/7272a4b4947d807a2b7de4a9f92fdb01a3ce3b69.jpg"},{"name":"Stage